    "created_at": "2015-10-20T19:30:11Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-20T19:45:50Z",
    "body": "The problem is only existent when the app resizes itself. It works properly when the size is changed by user interaction (dragging the window handle). I can't test it on win 8.\n\nMore details:\nOn startup the app has a size of e.g. 800x600 then the app recognized that the user is not logged in. The app prepares for showing the login screen and will resize itself (done by javascript) to a smaller size e.g. 200x600. While the app resizes itself it hangs. The same applies when the user triggers the automatic resize with e.g. a menu item (Sign out).\n"
